{"tid":1812071,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鳩拉48小時 = 支那行政拘留15日","createTime":"2020-01-05T08:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T09:10:25.000Z","uid":194298,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2b6accf35a7906fd6ab8b072dbccc0b0bbbd21d3","tid":1812071,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:42:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">行政拘留</span></strong>是最嚴厲的一種行政處罰，通常適用於<ins>嚴重違反治安管理<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但不構成犯罪</span></strong>，而警告、罰款處罰不足以懲戒的情況</ins>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">毋需原因，毋需理由<br />\n隨時可以限制你自由15日<br />\n香港受於現時法例所限只做到48小時<br />\n大力宣傳支那式純治，一國兩制已澈底玩完</span>"},{"pid":"8e684780e2905af582305fef1ecfff7538f619c2","tid":1812071,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ec54e0a30cfe992e7f36b310b4171b5cb5771cb2","tid":1812071,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:43:55.000Z","msg":"old news"},{"pid":"77c1b6c5f05dc54d2715aae58512c1c4e90dbc34","tid":1812071,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:53:45.000Z","msg":"港共已經將支那方式引入香港作管治"},{"pid":"d1bb96565492204201e387dc1519bbbce8464ffe","tid":1812071,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:56:02.000Z","msg":"咁又點？ 講個笑話你聽  香港人反抗"},{"pid":"ab65406001dee87eea632b817347e2238323c390","tid":1812071,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1bb96565492204201e387dc1519bbbce8464ffe","tid":1812071,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:56:02.000Z","msg":"咁又點？ 講個笑話你聽  香港人反抗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"閱"}]}